                     <interp inst="def1-38-18731124" type="given" value="CORNELIUS"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">CORNELIUS GRAY</hi> (23)</persName>
                  <rs id="t18731124-38-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18731124-38-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18731124-38-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>, Stealing a gelding, a van, and a set ofharness, the property of <persName id="t18731124-name-195" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18731124-name-195" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18731124-name-195" type="surname" value="HARVEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18731124-name-195" type="given" value="GEORGE WILLIAM"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18731124-38-offence-1 t18731124-name-195"></join>George William Harvey</persName>.</rs>
